name: Skriptbridge
tagline: A Skript add-on which hooks a bunch of plugins.
body:
### Welcome to SkriptBridge's Github Page
Skript bridge is an awesome add-on for Skript that adds support for many other plugins. If you want to check out the code or read the documentation, you've came to the right place. To download the code, simply click right over there in the right hand side of this page. To read the documentation, [click this link](https://github.com/joeuguce99/SkriptBridge/wiki).
